    "title": "Supply Chain Manager - TransIndia Logistics - Experienced Professionals",
    "description": "Join the TransIndia Logistics family as a Supply Chain Manager in Jabalpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout TransIndia Logistics:\nTransIndia Logistics is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Referral bonus program\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with TransIndia Logistics!",
